Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell[TextData[{
 "PHGN 515: Computational Project 2\n",
 StyleBox["White Light Interferometry",
  FontSize->24,
  FontWeight->"Regular"]
}], "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7552740620598*^9, 3.755274072243856*^9}, {
  3.755274695714754*^9, 3.75527469712357*^9}, {3.8718314716702223`*^9, 
  3.8718314729406967`*^9}, {3.8725532352753487`*^9, 
  3.872553240203487*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"95b37303-6677-49b6-b09c-\
f0b2eb614c5e"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Project Summary", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.755274163607428*^9, 
  3.755274166357678*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cc01a570-c85f-4d2d-b15f-\
a3e195226d45"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Scanning white light interferometry (WLI) is a versatile measurement tool. \
WLI can be used to measure the complex refractive index of materials and \
forms the basis for ",
 ButtonBox["optical coherence tomography",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optical_coherence_tomography"], None},
  ButtonNote->"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optical_coherence_tomography"],
 ". The goal of this project is to simulate scanning white light \
interferometry. Specifically, the goal is to computationally reconstruct the \
electric field in the frequency domain,  ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    OverscriptBox["E", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "f6627693-6f04-4b10-8d85-d737c7d7d198"],
 ", for two input time domain signal, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["E", "1"], "(", "t", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "01639c2d-fbdc-4dbc-997c-ccf26706054a"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["E", "2"], "(", "t", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "a6515354-4247-402b-b802-d52d7d23cd5d"],
 ". \n\nIn this project, you will reconstruct the frequency domain electric \
field for time domain electric fields ",
 StyleBox["provided by me",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " in the file, \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]electricFields.csv\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]. The format of the file is (as column vectors): time \
axis [fs], ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["E", "1"], "(", "t", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "67f20e32-4b1b-4d37-9101-7cf95eac4607"],
 " [a.u.], ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["E", "2"], "(", "t", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "e6cb2d07-287d-475b-8fe9-7b4afb075136"],
 " [a.u.]. You will then fit an ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["n", "th"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "d9ce9c3e-2686-472b-9ec8-a6fa0b6515ae"],
 " order polynomial to the spectral phase you recover and use the second \
order coefficient to estimate material composition. Finally, you will \
calculate the second moment, skewness, and kurtosis of the resulting spectrum."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7552741528068542`*^9, 3.75527415801682*^9}, {
   3.7552742810456867`*^9, 3.755274291135635*^9}, {3.755274408601207*^9, 
   3.755274418462164*^9}, {3.755274487639176*^9, 3.7552745068734083`*^9}, {
   3.755282155565679*^9, 3.75528222686957*^9}, {3.755282372829183*^9, 
   3.7552823868703613`*^9}, {3.755283771377837*^9, 3.7552837714499607`*^9}, {
   3.755286700300742*^9, 3.755286707074732*^9}, {3.871832313787149*^9, 
   3.871832318438406*^9}, {3.871833082934278*^9, 3.8718331178068867`*^9}, {
   3.87183568785331*^9, 3.871835719823183*^9}, {3.87183578086307*^9, 
   3.871835826237541*^9}, {3.8718358783145647`*^9, 3.8718359064345207`*^9}, {
   3.8718359405164833`*^9, 3.871835986560687*^9}, {3.8718496200170107`*^9, 
   3.871849697690151*^9}, {3.871852149171007*^9, 3.871852188999384*^9}, {
   3.8718523767864313`*^9, 3.871852390358218*^9}, {3.871852481804963*^9, 
   3.87185250170641*^9}, {3.87198393376117*^9, 3.8719839498063726`*^9}, 
   3.871992940426449*^9, {3.8719967355189667`*^9, 3.871996736605216*^9}, {
   3.8719968897773046`*^9, 3.871996912609743*^9}, {3.871997654405799*^9, 
   3.871997708831987*^9}, {3.871997787137072*^9, 3.871997794202962*^9}, {
   3.871998674366283*^9, 3.871998689105633*^9}, {3.8719987969459333`*^9, 
   3.871998871997724*^9}, {3.871999093247621*^9, 3.871999105896625*^9}, {
   3.872000258185336*^9, 3.87200027172014*^9}, {3.872000318703369*^9, 
   3.872000323867539*^9}, {3.872000554963278*^9, 3.872000558634139*^9}, {
   3.872000665811365*^9, 3.872000699574318*^9}, {3.872000800054687*^9, 
   3.872000800988744*^9}, {3.872001013881432*^9, 3.872001039344902*^9}, {
   3.872550328967659*^9, 3.872550340718539*^9}, {3.872551220990292*^9, 
   3.872551297181542*^9}, {3.872586432929514*^9, 3.87258643303738*^9}, {
   3.87258646907666*^9, 
   3.872586527214089*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"50991e19-0379-4ed7-88c9-\
bcb84a2fb5b4"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Scanning White Light Interferometry (WLI) Theory", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.871835910224997*^9, 3.871835937650309*^9}, {
  3.871846584882475*^9, 
  3.871846586244347*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fed6452d-294b-4aff-b46d-\
3f9f64b9c83a"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Simple case: No phase or amplitude difference", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.871846497748831*^9, 3.871846509479808*^9}, {
  3.871849728540373*^9, 
  3.871849728641395*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5c64fc40-6663-4766-968a-\
77c1396248f6"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "We first define a Fourier transform pair as\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      OverscriptBox["F", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"f", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], 
        SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "\[Omega]", " ", "\[Tau]"}]], 
        RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}]}], " ", "\[Congruent]", " ", 
      "\[ScriptCapitalF]"}]}], "\[InvisibleComma]", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"f", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "}"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"7e31d438-1f3d-4434-b079-7f6496a6423e"],
 "\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"f", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       FractionBox["1", 
        RowBox[{"2", "\[Pi]"}]], 
       RowBox[{
        SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          OverscriptBox["F", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", "\[Omega]", " ", "\[Tau]"}]], 
         RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Omega]"}]}]}]}], " ", "\[Congruent]", 
      " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[ScriptCapitalF]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "1"}]]}]}], "\[InvisibleComma]", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      OverscriptBox["F", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "}"}]}], 
   TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"74f7681a-aa17-4cfb-9c25-74f752ddaf19"],
 "\n\nThen, generally speaking, the total field in WLI is the superposition \
of two fields, one from either arm of the interferometer\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["E", "T"], "(", "t", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["E", "1"], "(", "t", ")"}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["E", "2"], "(", "t", ")"}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"aa4b3a39-b7a7-404b-adfb-9fb5eab399c9"],
 "\n\nin the simplest case, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["E", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d6ce5451-ec2c-42cf-8997-bee75385e5bd"],
 " is just a shifted version of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["E", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f47625d3-c085-42d6-92e0-435df63cb502"],
 ", that is to say\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["E", "2"], "(", "t", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["E", "1"], "(", 
      RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], "=", 
     RowBox[{"E", "(", 
      RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"6c7027d3-946d-4677-8e42-4b4bdacc20be"],
 "\n\nThe action of the detector is to absolute value square the total field \
and then integrate over some period so that the time domain signal is\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "T"}], "/", "2"}], 
       RowBox[{"T", "/", "2"}]], 
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
         RowBox[{
          SubscriptBox["E", "T"], "(", "t", ")"}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], 
        "2"], 
       RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}], "\[TildeTilde]", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], "+", 
          RowBox[{"E", "(", 
           RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}]}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], 
        "2"], 
       RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"2a912aa1-86c6-4cc7-9de1-f15ab59c7df5"],
 "\n\n",
 StyleBox["THIS IS WHAT YOU SHOULD DO IN YOUR SIMULATION",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\n\nHere, we have made the approximation that the integration period is \
extremely long e.g., ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"T", " ", 
     SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ">>>", "1"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "8f632e25-27ff-48dc-b669-9b6d8bdf6a43"],
 ", where ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["T", TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "6233d827-3d88-422e-bc9b-db5b8a9d1be0"],
 " is the integration period and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "85324e4a-f0e2-4264-81d8-919df2cc3d4b"],
 " is the mean frequency of the white light. Continuing on, expanding the \
absolute value squared\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      SuperscriptBox[
       RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
        RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], "2"]}], "+", 
     
     SuperscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
       RowBox[{"E", "(", 
        RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], "2"], 
     "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], 
      SuperscriptBox[
       RowBox[{"E", "(", 
        RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], "*"]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox[
       RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], "*"], 
      RowBox[{"E", "(", 
       RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"9ecc0554-08e9-426e-8a83-f6da6822c7c9"],
 "\n\nthe first two integrals are constant, which we will define as ",
 StyleBox["C",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"C", "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], 
       SuperscriptBox[
        RowBox[{"E", "(", 
         RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], "*"]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox[
       RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], "*"], 
      RowBox[{"E", "(", 
       RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"db6fcaaa-0b30-4248-8441-731c55772dca"],
 "\n\nwe now write the electric field as\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"E", "(", "t", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], 
     SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
      RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
       SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "t"}]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"9d621a97-504f-4b1f-b81d-767f0a5978aa"],
 "\n\nwhere ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "8a033839-d035-4207-aac9-6e314284fd10"],
 " is a complex amplitude (e.g., it can carry a phase). Substituting this \
into our expression,\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"C", "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
        RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
         SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "t"}]], 
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", 
        RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
         RowBox[{
          SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "(", 
          RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}]}]]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", "t", ")"}], 
      SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "t"}]], 
      RowBox[{"A", "(", 
       RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
      SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
       RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
        RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "(", 
         RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}]}]], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"5d83c016-4a50-4432-b41a-151235185f45"],
 "\n\nsimplifying\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"C", "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], 
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", 
        RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
        RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
         SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "\[Tau]"}]]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", "t", ")"}], 
      RowBox[{"A", "(", 
       RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
      SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "\[Tau]"}]], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"35936d6d-6dc0-4e38-855d-59641cd62a7c"],
 "\n\nit is instructive to see that when A is purely real, the signal is \
composed of a constant, C, and an oscillating function times the \
autocorrelation of the temporal envelop\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   StyleBox[
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "=", 
     RowBox[{"C", "+", 
      RowBox[{"2", 
       RowBox[{"cos", "(", 
        RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
       RowBox[{
        SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], 
         RowBox[{"A", "(", 
          RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], " ", 
         RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}]}]}],
    FontWeight->"Bold"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8007becd-d471-477d-83d3-2bbf8ed59f08"],
 "\n\n",
 StyleBox["YOU SHOULD SEE SOMETHING LIKE THIS IN YOUR SIMULATION",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\n\nand now taking the Fourier transform from \[Tau] \[LongLeftRightArrow] \
\[Omega] by multiplying the entire expression by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "\[Omega]", " ", "\[Tau]"}]], 
   TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"b287f756-710a-4241-bc65-8724521b7639"],
 " and integrating over \[Tau]\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"C", " ", 
      RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{
        SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", 
          RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
           SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "\[Tau]"}]], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "\[Omega]", " ", "\[Tau]"}]], 
         
         RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}]}], "]"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", "t", ")"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{
        SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"A", "(", 
          RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
           SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], "\[Tau]"}]], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "\[Omega]", " ", "\[Tau]"}]], 
         
         RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}]}], "]"}], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"0b5efebd-746e-4f73-902e-1c5a55e0878c"],
 "\n\nwhere I have defined ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "\[Congruent]", 
     "\[ScriptCapitalF]"}], "\[InvisibleComma]", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"I", "(", "\[Tau]", ")"}], "}"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "28a7ad33-76b0-4a81-8d5b-83ea6cbae8db"],
 ", simplifying \n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"C", " ", 
      RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{
        SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", 
          RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "\[Tau]", " ", 
           RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
             SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
         RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}]}], "]"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", "t", ")"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{
        SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"A", "(", 
          RowBox[{"t", "-", "\[Tau]"}], ")"}], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
           RowBox[{"\[Tau]", "(", 
            RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "+", 
             SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
         RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}]}], "]"}], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"72670fe3-ac09-4b27-9ec0-c301fb0138e9"],
 "\n\nwe see that this is actually computing the Fourier transforms from \
\[Tau] \[LongLeftRightArrow] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "\[PlusMinus]", 
    SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f2f6d249-2d17-4b91-a06a-d00f968e7d53"],
 ". Defining\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"u", "\[Congruent]", 
    RowBox[{"\[Tau]", "-", "t"}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "5558657b-3953-4179-af09-39bdfb3ab468"],
 "\tand\t",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "u"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "\[Tau]"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"b43e8627-23f7-4579-ac56-4d1cc3b73313"],
 "\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"C", " ", 
      RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
       RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "t", " ", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
            SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
        RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
          RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{
           SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", 
           RowBox[{"-", "u"}], ")"}], 
          SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "u", " ", 
            RowBox[{"(", 
             RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
              SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
          RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "u"}]}]}]}], "]"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", "t", ")"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{
        SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "t", " ", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "+", 
            SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
        RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
          RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"A", "(", 
           RowBox[{"-", "u"}], ")"}], 
          SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "u", " ", 
            RowBox[{"(", 
             RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "+", 
              SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
          RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "u"}]}]}]}], "]"}], 
      RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"4a39f3fd-4984-4872-bbbb-289696c12083"],
 "\n\nthe Fourier transforms evaluate to\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"C", " ", 
      RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "*"], "(", 
       RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{
       SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"A", "(", "t", ")"}], 
        SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
          RowBox[{"t", "(", 
           RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
            SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
        RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "(", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Omega]"}], "-", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{
       SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", 
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Infinity]"}], "\[Infinity]"], 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox["A", "*"], "(", "t", ")"}], 
        SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", 
          RowBox[{"t", "(", 
           RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "+", 
            SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]], 
        RowBox[{"\[DifferentialD]", "t"}]}]}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"854c4754-b5d9-4e80-8b41-79406d539956"],
 "\n\nand we note the remaining integrals are Fourier transforms as well, \
which we evaluate to give\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"C", " ", 
      RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "*"], "(", 
       RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{
       OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "(", 
       RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "(", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Omega]"}], "-", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}], 
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "*"], "(", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Omega]"}], "-", 
        SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}]}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"ddcc51db-01f5-440a-b062-3a722d51622f"],
 "\n\nwhich is\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox["I", "~"], "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"C", " ", 
      RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "(", "\[Omega]", ")"}]}], "+", 
     SuperscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
       RowBox[{
        OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "(", 
        RowBox[{"\[Omega]", "-", 
         SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], 
      "2"], "+", 
     SuperscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
       RowBox[{
        OverscriptBox["A", "~"], "(", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", "\[Omega]"}], "-", 
         SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], ")"}], "\[RightBracketingBar]"}], 
      "2"]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"fcfdd7e8-2e30-42ca-a369-e16826808aec"],
 "\n\n",
 StyleBox["THIS IS WHAT YOU SHOULD GET IN YOUR SIMULATION",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\n\nIn this simple case, the Fourier transform of the time domain \
correlation produces two copies of the ",
 StyleBox["spectrum",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ". One of the copies is centered at ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "9b078643-b42e-4d89-baba-840db0731add"],
 " and is not flipped. The other copy is centered at ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"-", 
    SubscriptBox["\[Omega]", "0"]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "776f7cc4-d9a2-4aa0-9ea0-ca5c1cb29644"],
 " and is flipped. This is what you will recover in your simulation."
}], "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->CompressedData["
1:eJwdzl1IUwEcBfCruESRLUvFbIrzAzXFWZuzSN1WaGFpOVOMCmuVs2lN82Fl
BYVi9AURZPnRNsOZ0czNxuph4dqIoi6+SHGX5WoT8mG50E2vsah77sOfHxzO
