     "Student handed in a smooth stone they found while on a walk",
      ExpressionUUID->"23386812-9fb5-49cd-85f3-37e9e16ac0c6"]},
    {Cell[
     "Organization",ExpressionUUID->"8958e7d7-119c-4997-879c-455a7ab7790e"], 
     Cell["\<\
Publication quality with well thought out ideas grouped into logical \
sections. Code is organized with descriptive variable names, well commented, \
and includes a header\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"33cf7362-7b6e-40f8-bd86-d87e0332f83a"], Cell["\<\
Graduate level quality with well thought out ideas group into logical \
sections. Code is organized, well commented, and includes a header\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"b510a10f-beec-4834-9056-b26e0de4b8ff"], Cell["\<\
Ideas are organized into blocks but not organized in a contiguous manner. \
Code is organized, few comments, and does not include a header\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"df5c14e0-4693-4fd6-8b11-60cf14718a89"], Cell["\<\
Ideas are scattered. Code not organized\[LongDash]spaghetti code. no \
comments, no header, poor variable names\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"b2032f17-c46e-4a5a-885e-e58b1c967e1c"], Cell["\<\
Student did not turn in working code. Student did not attempt to get help\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"19a9b499-3540-4942-99bd-256b4785e3c7"]},
    {Cell[
     "Communication",ExpressionUUID->"96ac7b16-82e4-4f37-88dd-76e5c86cc291"], 
     Cell["\<\
Uses expert level language and domain-specific vocabulary drawing on ideas \
from resources including class material and text. Publication quality \
grammar, punctuation, appearence, and citations. Student motivates arguments \
with concise calculations that highlight key concepts.\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"b1fcbd0d-b4be-4b81-a0eb-e0d2b79264b7"], Cell["\<\
Graduate level textual descriptions including sources and some mathematical \
derivation. Student uses some domain-secific vocabulary and draws on ideas \
from resources including class material and text. Appropriated grammar, \
punctuation, and appearance\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"8d7c030f-7bd6-4d5b-8f0a-6293e7585520"], Cell["\<\
Good textual descriptions with a few sources. Limited motivation for \
conclusions with some grammar or punctuation mistakes.\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"87f5b2d6-5692-45d9-8e2c-b08bda974cba"], Cell["\<\
Few descriptions and limited sources. No motivation for conclusion with \
several grammar and punctuation mistakes\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"1a0991ad-d843-4df2-b0c2-5f358798c651"], Cell["\<\
Poor writing, littered with grammatical mistakes. Student did not convey any \
working knowledge of basic principles. Student did not attempt to get help.\
\>",ExpressionUUID->"243ef1b2-a6fe-4a3b-b040-36cac31b945d"]}
   },
